Cliffjumper nodded, "We may as well check it out, I have a strange
feeling." he mentioned. "Torca, come with me, the rest of you, rest."
Cliffjumper tranfsormed, and roared off at his top speed, accelerating
to 250mph towards the fiery shape, hoping Torca was following him for
backup.
